	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />That's close to 312/262*15/16 = 1.1164, presumably reflecting an assumption that the APU Frame Counter was supposed to keep the same ratio to a PPU frame on PAL as on NTSC. I have no PAL NES, or I'd make a test ROM.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
